p: In the District Court of the 3rd Judicial District in and for the County of King Territory of Washington.
In the matter of Frank OBrien Habeas Corpus

And now comes the said OBriend by his Atty John E. Costello and says that he is unable to procure the pennies of aan attorney for pay and that he is unable to pay necessary clerk fees up on the filing of his petition for writ of Habeas Corpus and asks to the same be filed.
by his Atty John E. Costello
